# Test & coverage artifacts
*.test
*.out
coverage.*
*.prof
*.pprof

# go.work is committed (repo-root workspace ties the 5 sql-adapter modules for
# local dev; see docs/RELEASE.md). go.work.sum is NOT committed: it accumulates
# transient checksums from whatever the workspace happens to have built locally
# (e.g. dbtest's testcontainers/docker closure) and isn't reproducibly stable
# across machines/clean checkouts — each module's own go.sum is authoritative.
go.work.sum

